# Scripts Directory

Place executable code (Python/Bash/etc.) here for tasks that require deterministic reliability.

## When to use

- When the same code is being rewritten repeatedly
- When deterministic reliability is needed
- When you want to save tokens by not loading code into context

## Examples

- `rotate_pdf.py` - PDF rotation utility
- `process_data.sh` - Data processing script

## Best practices

1. Keep scripts focused on a single task
2. Include clear usage instructions in comments
3. Test scripts before committing
4. Use parameters for flexibility
